# Module Spec: cli/quicksum.js

## Behaviour
- Parse numbers from process arguments.
- Validate inputs are finite numbers.
- Print the sum and append the message `Sum: <value>` to quicksum.log in the current directory.
- Log entries must include ISO timestamps.
- Exit with code 0 on success, 1 on invalid input.

## Implementation Notes
- Use Node.js built-in modules only.
- Export functions for reuse: parseArgs, computeTotal, appendLog, runCli.